import React from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import { User, Lock, Settings, LogOut } from 'lucide-react'; const Profile = ({ user, theme, onLogout }) => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const isDark = theme === 'dark'; const styles = { container: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#0f172a' : '#f8fafc', minHeight: '100%', fontFamily: "'Inter', sans-serif", padding: '40px', maxWidth: '1200px', margin: '0 auto' }, header: { marginBottom: '30px', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '15px' }, title: { fontSize: '28px', fontWeight: '800', color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b', lineHeight: '1.2' }, subtitle: { color: '#64748b', fontSize: '15px' }, grid: { display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: 'repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr))', gap: '30px', alignItems: 'start' }, // Left Identity Card identityCard: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#fff', borderRadius: '24px', padding: '40px 30px', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', boxShadow: '0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.03)', border: isDark ? '1px solid #334155' : '1px solid #e2e8f0' }, avatarWrapper: { width: '120px', height: '120px', borderRadius: '50%', padding: '4px', background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #ec4899)', marginBottom: '20px' }, avatar: { width: '100%', height: '100%', borderRadius: '50%', objectFit: 'cover', border: '4px solid #fff', backgroundColor: '#f1f5f9' }, name: { fontSize: '24px', fontWeight: '800', color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b', marginBottom: '5px' }, email: { color: '#64748b', marginBottom: '20px' }, badge: { backgroundColor: '#eff6ff', color: '#4f46e5', padding: '8px 20px', borderRadius: '20px', fontSize: '13px', fontWeight: '700', border: '1px solid #c7d2fe' }, // Right Column rightColumn: { display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: '24px' }, detailsBox: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#fff', borderRadius: '20px', padding: '30px', boxShadow: '0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.02)', border: isDark ? '1px solid #334155' : '1px solid #e2e8f0' }, sectionTitle: { fontSize: '18px', fontWeight: 'bold', marginBottom: '20px', color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b' }, detailRow: { display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'space-between', padding: '15px 0', borderBottom: isDark ? '1px solid #334155' : '1px solid #f1f5f9' }, detailLabel: { color: '#94a3b8', fontSize: '14px', fontWeight: '600' }, detailValue: { color: isDark ? '#fff' : '#1e293b', fontWeight: '700', fontSize: '15px' }, actionsGrid: { display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: 'repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr))', gap: '20px' }, actionCard: { backgroundColor: isDark ? '#1e293b' : '#fff', padding: '20px', borderRadius: '16px', cursor: 'pointer', border: isDark ? '1px solid #334155' : '1px solid #e2e8f0', transition: 'all 0.2s', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '15px' }, iconBox: (color, bg) => ({ width: '45px', height: '45px', borderRadius: '12px', backgroundColor: bg, color: color, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }) }; return (
